name: Alice Liddell (Disney)
description:
If you like the LoRa, please feel free to share your generated images here and leave a review (or at least a rating) for the sake of motivation and stuff ;D

For usage guidance, look into the About this version box for more information and click on Show more to get all trigger words and combinations (The trigger words in the Details box are a pain to manage).

Please contact me here on civitAi or on Twitter if you want to provide the LoRa in a generation service.

About

Well, not much to say... It is Alice from Disney's Alice in Wonderland. I would really like to make a Lora of this old (non-Disney) anime adaptation of this story (which brings back childhood memories), but I can't find it... Well, one day I will.

Training

I collected 55 pictures of Alice... To be honest, it was painful. It's such a weird story with too many weird characters. (And I still don't get it). This model is not going to provide any variety on the outfit front. Simply because Alice is wearing her well-known Alice costume.

I deleted V1 training data and already trained model by accident so I had to do the whole thing again ;_;

How to use the LoRa

Basic prompt:

alice liddell, blue dress, white apron, black hairband, white legwear, black shoes <lora:alice_liddell_v20:1>

meta.prompt: (masterpiece:1.4), (best qualit:1.4), (high resolution:1.4), alice liddell, blue dress, white apron, black hairband, smile, looking at viewer, <lora:alice_liddell_v2:1>
